{"tid":136395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自比猶太人警隸屬「速龍小隊」 曾處理佔領清場","createTime":"2017-02-27T04:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T06:52:32.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55075a18fb5afac2b84b9fd922821050ef555bd2","tid":136395,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170227/large/1488169625_2335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170227%2Flarge%2F1488169625_2335.jpg&h=46b57ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有警員以納粹德軍迫害的猶太人事件比喻警員被侮辱，事件持續發酵，繼德國及以色列駐港領事館發聲明，以色列主要報章亦有報道事件；據《南華早報》報道，該名上台發言警員原來隸屬「速龍小隊」﹙the elite Special Tactical Squad﹚，並任警署警長﹙station sergeant﹚。<br />\n<br />\n發表自比猶太人言論的姓陳警員，自稱是警察員佐級協會會員。他早前在台上發言時指，警務人員執勤時常被侮辱，經常「要帶住屋企人返工」，更形容「家好似二次世界大戰，我哋係猶太人，我哋家被迫害緊，被德國納粹軍隊迫害嘅猶太人咁嘅心態、情況，啱唔啱？」全場集會人士即回答：「啱！」當時坐在姓陳警員身後的警司協會主席郭柏聰亦有點頭。<br />\n<br />\n相關言論引起各界關注及批評，以色列及德國駐港領事館公別回應事件，指有關言論不恰當令人遺憾（inappropriate and regretful），更直斥是對歷史事實無知﹙a regrettably insufficient knowledge of historical facts﹚。<br />\n<br />\n「速龍小隊」由反恐特勤隊、機場特警及機動部隊及槍械訓練教官組成，裝備包括防暴頭盔、防毒面具、手套及索帶等等。「速龍小隊」的特別戰術小隊控制場面。「速龍小隊」為數50至60人，於佔領行動期間，主力協助清場的工作。<br />\n<br />\n「警署警長」(Station Sergeant)是香港警察職級中最高級員佐級職級，為初級警務人員的級別；位於警長之上，見習督察之下，負責擔任小隊指揮官或小隊副指揮官。"},{"pid":"adee33afa3331bbdae38bc056a012c38e9244e70","tid":136395,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ac8eecea05ab429cfb1525a98caa053e8f8598","tid":136395,"uid":9342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"醜死怪，又渠出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9741f23e38fbde3856068dced58a7086e3c0d4","tid":136395,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"114bc2e6059dbeab9a923dfed39fb63ddcb8151d","tid":136395,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係曲線串緊當年既猶太人無撚用?"},{"pid":"f52030d3aeecdb8099ed9043d688c5b9abc168f3","tid":136395,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"比人打到仆街果班速龍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ec50db124dc0a175f74f0dab663a8444d97dd4","tid":136395,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人打到仆街果班速龍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n義士一還手, 即刻爆缸畜膿<br />\n<br />\n佢地係「速龍」定「畜膿」,, 係視乎義士選唔選擇打柒佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160212/large/12la4p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160212%2Flarge%2F12la4p1.jpg&h=98f0886d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}